# Styling

## Tokens

Use theme from `tailwind.config.js`:

- `primary` `#050816`, `secondary`, `tertiary`, `black-100`, `black-200`, `white-100`
- Accent purple: `#915EFF` (hero highlight)

## Patterns

- Gradients: `violet-gradient`, `green-pink-gradient`, `black-gradient` in `src/index.css`
- Section padding: `styles.padding` / `styles.paddingX` from `src/styles.js`

## Hero background

- Prefer CSS gradient over broken asset paths
- Do not reference `/src/assets/herobg.png` in Tailwind unless file exists and is imported

## Responsive

- Test `xs` (450px) and mobile Skills split at 768px
